      <title>DS100学习记录</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/25/DS100%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/25/DS100%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="DS100学习笔记"><a href="#DS100学习笔记" class="headerlink" title="DS100学习笔记"></a>DS100学习笔记</h1><h2 id="1-jupyter-notebook基本操作"><a href="#1-jupyter-notebook基本操作" class="headerlink" title="1.jupyter notebook基本操作"></a>1.jupyter notebook基本操作</h2><h3 id="Keyboard-Shortcuts："><a href="#Keyboard-Shortcuts：" class="headerlink" title="Keyboard Shortcuts："></a>Keyboard Shortcuts：</h3><ol><li><code>Ctrl</code> + <code>Return</code>: <em>Evaluate the current cell</em></li><li><code>Shift</code> + <code>Return</code>: <em>Evaluate the current cell and move to the next</em></li><li><code>ESC</code> : <em>command mode</em> (may need to press before using any of the commands below)</li><li><code>a</code> : <em>create a cell above</em></li><li><code>b</code> : <em>create a cell below</em></li><li><code>dd</code> : <em>delete a cell</em></li><li><code>z</code> : <em>undo the last cell operation</em></li><li><code>m</code> : <em>convert a cell to markdown</em></li><li><code>y</code> : <em>convert a cell to code</em></li></ol><h3 id="编写shell脚本解决报错问题："><a href="#编写shell脚本解决报错问题：" class="headerlink" title="编写shell脚本解决报错问题："></a>编写shell脚本解决报错问题：</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">! /bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line">sed &#x27;1i OK_FORMAT = True&#x27; *.py -i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过 <code>chmod +x</code>命令给予执行权限并执行。</p><h2 id="2-numpy学习"><a href="#2-numpy学习" class="headerlink" title="2.numpy学习"></a>2.numpy学习</h2><p>基础：将其他如list元素转化为numpy np.array()</p><h3 id="1-元素寻找"><a href="#1-元素寻找" class="headerlink" title="1.元素寻找"></a>1.元素寻找</h3><p>1.np.[condition] or np.where(conditon, [x,y])</p><h2 id="3-pandas学习"><a href="#3-pandas学习" class="headerlink" title="3.pandas学习"></a>3.pandas学习</h2><h2 id="4-matplotlib学习"><a href="#4-matplotlib学习" class="headerlink" title="4.matplotlib学习"></a>4.matplotlib学习</h2><h2 id="5-Latex学习"><a href="#5-Latex学习" class="headerlink" title="5.Latex学习"></a>5.Latex学习</h2><p>基础：<br>$$<br>\sum_{i&#x3D;0}^n i^3<br>$$</p><p>$$<br>\begin{align}<br>f(x)&amp;&#x3D;(x-1)^2\<br>&amp;&#x3D;x^2-2x+1<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p><p>$$<br>\sum_{i&#x3D;1}^n(a_i+b_i)&#x3D;\frac{1}{\sum_{i&#x3D;1}^na_i}+\sum_{i&#x3D;1}^nb_i<br>$$</p><p>$$<br>\begin{align}1-\sigma(x)&amp;&#x3D;\frac{1+e^{-x}-1}{1+e^{-x}}\<br>&amp;&#x3D;\frac{e^{-x}}{1+e^{-x}}\<br>&amp;&#x3D;\frac{1}{e^x+1}\<br>&amp;&#x3D;\sigma(-x)<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
